s%20that%20about%20her.%26quot%3B%20I%20like%20to%20think%20that's%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-new-apartment-got-married-wedding-same-week-stress-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709470141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e23f1dce7f1785b2e59a66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-new-apartment-got-married-wedding-same-week-stress-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20into%20a%20new%20apartment%20a%20week%20before%20our%20wedding.%20It%20could've%20been%20stressful%2C%20but%20it%20made%20us%20closer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Hayley%20Folk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Unions%20Announce%20March%20Towards%20Delhi%20via%20Road%2C%20Air%20and%20on%20Foot%20on%20March%206%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20the%20%3Cem%3Eantim%20bhog%3C%2Fem%3E%20ceremony%20of%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-shubhkaran-singh%5C%22%3Ekilled%20during%20clashes%20between%20farmers%20and%20security%20forces%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20farmer%20bodies%20leading%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Challo%E2%80%99%20programme%20announced%20that%20they%20will%20be%20heading%20to%20the%20capital%20on%20March%206%20by%20train%2C%20bus%2C%20air%20and%20foot%20to%20step%20up%20pressure%20on%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EJagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20convener%20of%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM%20non-political)%2C%20who%20is%20leading%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%20Punjab%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20often%20asked%20farmers%20to%20march%20peacefully%20to%20Delhi%20without%20their%20tractor-trolleys.%20In%20line%20with%20this%2C%20the%20farmers%20have%20changed%20their%20strategy%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20through%20other%20means.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20now%20see%20how%20farmers%20are%20treated%20in%20Delhi%20and%20whether%20we%20are%20allowed%20to%20protest%20peacefully%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EDallewal%20also%20announced%20a%20one-day%20%E2%80%98rail-roko%E2%80%99%20program%20on%20March%2010%2C%20between%2012%20pm%20and%204%20pm%2C%20as%20part%20of%20their%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20that%20this%20agitation%20is%20not%20of%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20or%20Shubhkaran%20alone.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20national%20agitation%20and%20they%20must%20support%20their%20cause.%20He%20said%20this%20country%20will%20grow%20if%20farmers%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20has%20been%20a%20key%20demand%20of%20farmer%20unions%2C%20which%20they%20claimed%20was%20promised%20by%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20time%20of%20withdrawing%20three%20farm%20laws%20during%20last%20edition%20of%20farm%20protest%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESince%20the%20demand%20has%20remained%20unfulfilled%2C%20farmers%20unions%2C%20mainly%20splinter%20groups%20of%20SKM%20(which%20played%20key%20role%20in%202020%20farm%20protest)%20began%20marching%20towards%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%20from%20various%20towns%20of%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20security%20forces%20deployed%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20at%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20halted%20their%20march%20by%20dropping%20tear%20gas%20shells%20and%20other%20excessive%20use%20of%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EIn%20several%20rounds%20of%20clashes%20since%20then%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20farmers%20as%20well%20as%20policemen%20have%20sustained%20serious%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20them%20was%2022-year-old%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%20from%20Bhatinda%E2%80%99s%20Ballo%20village%20who%20died%20during%20these%20clashes%20at%20Khanuari%20border%20on%20February%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHis%20body%20was%20only%20cremated%20a%20week%20later%2C%20on%20February%2029%2C%20after%20Punjab%20police%20filed%20a%20murder%20case%20under%20pressure%20from%20farmer%20bodies.%C2%A0%20As%20per%20media%20reports%2C%20an%20autopsy%20report%20also%20confirmed%20the%20initial%20suspicion%20that%20he%20had%20died%20of%20a%20firearm%20injury%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStir%20to%20continue%20on%20borders%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20convener%20of%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%2C%20which%20is%20also%20leading%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20march%2C%20also%20told%20media%20that%20their%20protest%20would%20continue%20at%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20number%20of%20farmers%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khannauri%20is%20set%20to%20increase%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%20border%20points%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20would%20also%20be%20covered%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EPandher%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20way%20that%20farmers%20will%20step%20back%20from%20their%20protest.%20They%20will%20fight%20till%20they%20get%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20non-negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%