%20Michael%2C%20Konthoujam%20Romojit%20Meitei%20alias%20Romojit%20and%20Keisham%20Johnson%20alias%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20transferred%20by%20the%20state%20government%20to%20the%20central%20agency%20on%20August%2024%20last%20year.%20The%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20so%20far%20transferred%2029%20cases%20to%20the%20CBI.%20As%20per%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20these%20cases%20are%20being%20tried%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20Assam%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20case%20is%20one%20among%20several%20others%20related%20to%20the%20looting%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20from%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20valley%20districts%20of%20Manipur%20during%20the%20ethnic%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20Kangpokpi%20district%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-assembly-adopts-resolution-to-abrogate-soo-deal-with-kuki-outfits-101709217505619.html%5C%22%3Eis%20set%20to%20witness%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20shutdown%20on%20March%204%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%E2%80%99s%20adoption%20of%20a%20resolution%20on%20February%2029.%20The%20resolution%20aims%20to%20abrogate%20the%20suspension%20of%20operation%20(SoO)%20with%2025%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%20by%20the%20Centre%20on%20grounds%20of%20violation%20of%20rules%20of%20the%20agreement.%20The%20six-month%20validity%20of%20the%20SoO%20with%20the%20Centre%20was%20to%20expire%20on%20February%2029.%20Notably%2C%20no%20Kuki%20MLA%20was%20present%20in%20the%20House%20when%20the%20resolution%20was%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20had%20decided%20to%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20days%20before%20the%20ethnic%20strife%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20the%20Kuki%20communities%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20continued%20with%20the%20arrangement.%20In%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20several%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20groups%20have%20petitioned%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20to%20reconsider%20this%20decision.%20The%20Centre%20has%20so%20far%20kept%20quiet%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20day-long%20shutdown%2C%20the%20civil%20society%20group%2C%20Committee%20for%20Tribal%20Unity%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-shutdown-against-soo-resolution%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20decided%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20take%20out%20a%20rally%20against%20the%20assembly%E2%80%99s%20resolution%20on%20March%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709467256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcbi-files-chargesheets-in-manipur-arms-looting-case-six-months-after-taking-over%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20case%20was%20transferred%20by%20the%20state%20government%20to%20the%20central%20agency%20on%20August%2024%20last%20year.%20The%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20so%20far%20transferred%2029%20cases%20to%20the%20CBI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcbi-files-chargesheets-in-manipur-arms-looting-case-six-months-after-taking-over%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20CEO%20wants%20to%20kill%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224358%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20chat%20at%20a%20job%20fair%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bbf7667a3d27148876c923%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinding%20a%20job%20often%20involves%20using%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20Advocates%20say%20there%20are%20better%20approaches.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Slitz%2FAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKhyati