A6%20We%20gave%20them%20power.%20In%20this%20Gandhi%20maidan%20only%20we%20brought%20all%20backward%20classes%20and%20told%20them%20to%20address%20rallies%20and%20not%20just%20in%20Bihar%20but%20in%20all%20of%20country%20we%20applied%20Mandal%20Commission.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20those%20who%20call%20themselves%20big%20people%20can%20not%20show%20eyes%20to%20the%20poor.%20At%20that%20time%20there%20used%20to%20be%20wells.%20If%20anyone%20from%20upper%20caste%20used%20a%20well%20and%20a%20lower%20caste%20tried%20to%20use%20that%20well%2C%20then%20they%20were%20shooed%20away.%20The%20well%20was%20emptied%20and%20was%20only%20used%20when%20all%20the%20water%20was%20thrown%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ELalu%20said%20%E2%80%9CI%20say%20here%2C%20at%20Gandhi%20maidan%2C%20with%20confidence%20that%20BJP%20will%20be%20ousted%20at%20the%20incoming%20polls.%E2%80%9D%20He%20raised%20a%20slogan%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CDilli%20pe%20qabza%20karna%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20Narendra%20Modi%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20asked%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%20is%20he%20going%20on%20about%20%3Cem%3Eparivarwaad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20taunting%20those%20with%20families%3F%E2%80%9D%20Modi%2C%20he%20said%20was%20only%20spreading%20animus%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENafrat%20phailaa%20rahe%20ho%3F%20Ram%20Rahim%20ke%20bandon%20mein.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20said%20Lalu%2C%20%E2%80%9Call%20manner%20of%20greats%20have%20been%20born%2C%20just%20here%20in%20Gandhi%20maidan%2C%20national%20leaders%20have%20held%20meetings.%20And%20it%20is%20from%20here%20that%20messages%20go%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20what%20will%20happen%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMera%20kidney%20ka%20transplant%20hua%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20my%20daughter%20Rohini%20Acharya%20gave%20me%20her%20kidney%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20acknowledged.%20Mentioning%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20ask%20every%20evening%2C%20how%20many%20jobs%20have%20you%20given%3F%20Get%20reservations%20among%20soldiers%2C%20so%20there%20would%20be%20better%20representations%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20abused%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20I%20just%20said%20he%20is%20%3Cem%3Epaltu%20%3C%2Fem%3ERam%20%3Cem%3E(pet)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Second%20time%2C%20I%20erred%2C%20Tejashwi%20erred%20too%2C%20as%20he%20came%20to%20us%2C%20but%20he%20went%20back%20to%20take%20refuge%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20feet.%20Is%20he%20not%20ashamed%20to%20see%20all%20the%20memes%20we%20get%20on%20the%20phone%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20was%20received%20with%20enthusiasm%20and%20underlined%20the%20cronyism%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20as%20one%20favouring%20billionaires%2C%20writing%20off%20loans%20of%20big%20industrialists%2C%20while%20totally%20disregarding%20the%20backwards%20in%20the%20country%2C%20not%20giving%20them%20their%20share.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20afraid%20of%20BJP-RSS%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20die%20for%20country%20and%20make%20an%20INDIA%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKharge%20addressed%20Modi%20and%20paltu%20chacha%2C%20with%20a%20rhyme%2C%20calling%20out%20their%20%E2%80%9Clies%E2%80%9D.%20He%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20struggle%2C%20to%20fight%20in%20the%20days%20ahead%2C%20and%20win%20the%20coming%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CINDIA%20bloc%20people%20do%20what%20they%20say.%20Today%20INDIA%20is%20fighting%20Modi.%20Till%20the%20time%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20remove%20Modi%2C%20the%20country%20will%20not%20prosper%E2%80%A6%20If%20you%20would%20not%20remove%20Modi%20then%20democracy%2C%20constitution%20will%20not%20survive.%20I%20It%20is%20your%20duty%20to%20save%20our%20constitution.%E2%80%9D%20He%20asserted%20that%20no%20one%20would%20be%20subdued%20by%20action%20of%20central%20agencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0CPI(ML)%E2%80%99s%20Bhattacharya%20invoked%20famous%20lines%20of%20Hindi%20writer%20Ramdhari%20Singh%20Dinkar%2C%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSinghasan%20khali%20karo%2C%20ki%20Janta%20aati%20hai%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20vacate%20your%20throne%2C%20as%20the%20people%20are%20here.%20He%20pointed%20out%20to%20the%20celebrations%20of%20the%20pre-wedding%20of%20billionaire%20Mukesh%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20son%20being%20facilitated%2C%20versus%20thousands%20of%20farmers%2C%20despite%20several%20losing%20their%20lives%2C%20not%20being%20given%20a%20hearing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Modi%20hatao%20desh%20bachao%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20Yechury%2C%20as%20he%20spoke%20of%20false%20promises%20of%20Modi%20government%2C%20praising%20the%20Mahagatbandhan%20for%20jobs.%20He%20invoked%20the%20Puranic%20tale%20of%20%3Cem%3Eamrit%3C%2Fem%3E%20(elixir)%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20oceanic%20churn%2C%20passing%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwrong%20persons%E2%80%9D.%20The%20challenge%20he%20said%20was%20to%20get%20the%20amrit%20back%20and%20save%20India%20to%20ensure%20a%20better%20future%20for%20its%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20watch%20the%20rally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJzktUiRDcp0%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709465980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03170822%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-5.07.46-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frjds-jan-vishwas-patna-rally-turns-into-a-big-india-push-first-in-hindi-belt-in-2024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rally%20struck%20a%20defiant%20tone%20and%20laid%20down%20the%20parameters%20of%20the%20fight%20ahead%20%E2%80%93%20of%20rights%2C%20empo