C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20noted%20that%20an%20Israeli%20investigation%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Council%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20take%20all%20necessary%20measures%20to%20protect%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20parties%20to%20conflicts%20must%20comply%20with%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImmediate%20delivery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParties%20were%20urged%20to%20refrain%20from%20depriving%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20of%20basic%20services%20and%20humanitarian%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Council%20expressed%20grave%20concern%20that%20the%20entire%20population%2C%20more%20than%20two%20million%20people%2C%20could%20face%20alarming%20levels%20of%20acute%20food%20insecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20reiterated%20their%20demand%20for%20parties%20%E2%80%9Cto%20allow%2C%20facilitate%2C%20and%20enable%20the%20immediate%2C%20rapid%2C%20safe%2C%20sustained%20and%20unhindered%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20assistance%20at%20scale%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20civilian%20population%20throughout%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20urged%20Israel%20to%20keep%20border%20crossings%20open%20for%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20enter%20Gaza%2C%20to%20facilitate%20the%20opening%20of%20additional%20crossings%20to%20meet%20humanitarian%20needs%20at%20scale%2C%20and%20to%20support%20the%20rapid%20and%20safe%20delivery%20of%20relief%20items%20to%20people%20across%20the%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Airdrops%20close%20to%20worst%20ways%20to%20deliver%20aid%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20US%20military%20on%20Saturday%20carried%20out%20its%20first%20airdrop%20of%20aid%20into%20Gaza.%20Other%20countries%20including%20Jordan%20and%20France%20have%20already%20conducted%20airdrops%20of%20aid%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20airdrop%20used%20C-130%20transport%20aircraft%20which%20dropped%20more%20than%2038%2C000%20meals%20along%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20Mediterranean%20coastline%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus-carries-out-first-airdrop-aid-into-gaza-officials-say-2024-03-02%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20experts%20say%20this%20is%20the%20worst%20way%20to%20deliver%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20only%20resort%20to%20%5Bairdrops%5D%20when%20there%20is%20something%20on%20the%20ground%20blocking%20you%20from%20using%20better%20forms%20of%20transportation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jeremy%20Konyndyk%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Refugees%20International%20and%20a%20former%20disaster%20relief%20official%20in%20the%20%5Bformer%20US%20President%20Barack%5D%20Obama%20and%20%5BUS%20President%20Joe%5D%20Biden%20administrations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2024%2F3%2F3%2Fisraels-war-on-gaza-live-every-minute-counts-as-hunger-kills-in-gaza%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20Al%20Jazeera.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20very%20expensive%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20dangerous%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20that%20can%20go%20wrong%20when%20things%20drop%20and%20they%20deliver%20a%20very%20small%20volume%20of%20aid.%20Relative%20to%20the%20level%20of%20need%20that%20exists%20in%20Gaza%20today%2C%20this%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20make%20a%20meaningful%20dent%20in%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20ask%2C%20why%20is%20this%20necessary%3F%20Well%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20necessary%20because%20over%20the%20last%20nearly%20five%20months%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20offensive%20has%20made%20it%20virtually%20impossible%20for%20normal%20humanitarian%20operations%20to%20exist%20in%20Gaza%2C%E2%80%9D%20Konyndyk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20could%20be%20opening%20more%20border%20crossings%20%E2%80%93%20they%20have%20refused%20to%20do%20that.%20Even%20the%20tw