lice%20constable%20examination%20was%20cancelled%20also%20due%20to%20paper%20leak.%20Held%20on%20February%2017%20and%2018%2C%20that%20examination%20was%20cancelled%20after%20students%20held%20a%20massive%20protest%20in%20Lucknow%20demanding%20a%20re-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fup-police-special-task-force-stf-arrests-two-in-connection-with-police-recruitment-exam-paper-leak%2Fcid%2F2004330%5C%22%3Enews%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20two%20persons%20have%20been%20arrested%20so%20far%20by%20the%20special%20task%20force%20of%20UP%20Police%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20police%20constable%20examination%20paper%20leak%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recently%20held%20Class%2012%20examination%20by%20the%20state%20board%20too%20saw%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%2C%20sending%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20educational%20community.%20The%20maths%20and%20biology%20papers%20were%20available%20an%20hour%20after%20the%20examination%20on%20social%20media.%20Since%20they%20were%20leaked%20after%20the%20exam%20had%20started%2C%20the%20state%20board%20%E2%80%98denied%E2%80%99%20it%20to%20be%20a%20case%20of%20paper%20leak.%20The%20papers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Feducation%2Fup-board-upmsp-12th-inter-denies-paper-leak-allegation-math-biology-9189581%2F%5C%22%3Ewere%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india.com%2Feducation%2Fup-class-12th-board-paper-leak-2024-upmsp-cancels-recognition-of-college-responsible-for-maths-biology-question-paper-leak-6759192%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20have%20been%3C%2Fa%3E%20leaked%20through%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20by%20a%20college%20in%20Agra.%20The%20board%20has%20since%20de-recognised%20the%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20exam%20paper%20leak%20cases%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-ruled%20state%20frequently%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20snowballed%20into%20a%20political%20talking%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%202%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi-Vadra%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20news%20about%20the%20board%20examination%20paper%20leak%20reports%2C%20took%20to%20X%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CPaper%20leaked%20once%20again.%20Why%20after%20all.%20Under%20BJP%20rule%2C%20from%20job%20exams%20to%20board%20exams%20%E2%80%93%20almost%20every%20paper%20is%20getting%20leaked.%20Board%20examinations%20are%20the%20first%20challenges%20that%20children%20face%20when%20they%20learn%20to%20build%20their%20future.%20If%20such%20a%20big%20betrayal%20happens%20to%20them%20right%20here%2C%20what%20will%20they%20do%20next.%20To%20save%20the%20examination%20mafia%20and%20the%20corrupt%20people%20sitting%20in%20the%20government%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20also%20hollowing%20the%20foundation%20of%20crores%20of%20children%20and%20youth%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709458251000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03143757%2Fimage-1895.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-govt-cancels-ro-aro-exam-amid-paper-leak-allegations-job-aspirant-dies-by-suicide%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20cancel%20the%20RO%2FARO%20exams%20came%20just%20a%20week%20after%20the%20police%20constable%20examination%20was%20cancelled%20also%20due%20to%20paper%20leak.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-govt-cancels-ro-aro-exam-amid-paper-leak-allegations-job-aspirant-dies-by-suicide%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Norway's%20King%20Harald%20gets%20successful%20pacemaker%20implant%20surgery%20in%20Malaysia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709458198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108179253%2Cimgsize-861604.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiati