alia%20beat%20India%20in%20both%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20and%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20final%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20report%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20true%2C%20it%20would%20be%20another%20big%20change%20in%20captaincy%20in%20IPL.%20In%20December%20last%20year%2C%20five-time%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%20had%20replaced%20Rohit%20Sharma%20with%20Hardik%20Pandya%20in%20the%20captaincy%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20New%20Zealand%20left-arm%20pacer%20James%20Franklin%20is%20likely%20to%20replace%20Dale%20Steyn%20as%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20bowling%20coach%20in%20the%20upcoming%20IPL%2C%20beginning%20on%20March%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESteyn%2C%20a%20former%20South%20African%20fast%20bowler%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20SRH%20bowling%20coach%20in%202022%2C%20has%20requested%20the%20franchise%20to%20give%20him%20a%20break%20for%20this%20season%20owing%20to%20personal%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20talks%20with%20him%20(Franklin)%20as%20Dale%20Steyn%20will%20not%20be%20available%20for%20this%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20IPL%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2043-year-old%20had%20earlier%20played%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20the%202011%20and%202021%20seasons%2C%20but%20this%20is%20his%20maiden%20stint%20as%20coach%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFranklin%2C%20however%2C%20has%20coaching%20experience%20with%20Durham%20in%20English%20county%20cricket%20and%20Pakistan%20Super%20League%20team%20Islamabad%20United%20as%20assistant%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20SRH%2C%20Franklin%20will%20link%20up%20with%20his%20former%20teammate%20Daniel%20Vettori%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20team's%20head%20coach%20after%20IPL%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20they%20have%20worked%20together%20at%20Middlesex%20in%20county%20cricket%20as%20well%20as%20with%20Birmingham%20Phoenix%20in%20the%20Hundred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFranklin%20has%20played%2031%20Tests%2C%20110%20ODIs%20and%2038%20T20Is%20for%20New%20Zealand%20between%202001%20and%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709457720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fpb3l5h78_rohit-sharma-bcci_625x300_17_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fafter-rohit-sharma-another-captain-of-ex-champion-team-may-face-the-axe-report-5164730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20franchise%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20is%20expected%20to%20change%20its%20captain%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20edition%2C%20claimed%20a%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vedanta%20Resources%20to%20deleverage%20debt%20by%20%243%20billion%20over%203%20years%3A%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709457654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-12%2F29%2Ffull%2F1609235533-0889.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-resources-to-deleverage-debt-by-3-billion-over-3-years-official-124030300241_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20recently%20divested%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20its%20shares%20through%20its%20promoter%20entity%20Finsider%20International%2C%20and%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20strategic%20manoeuvring%20within%20the%20company%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-resources-to-deleverage-debt-by-3-billion-over-3-years-official-124030300241_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvedanta-resources-to-deleverage-debt-by-3-billion-over-3-years-offic