00w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03130107%2Funnamed-2-300x208.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03130107%2Funnamed-2-1024x708.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699900%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22830%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECourtesy%20Ashoka%20Archives%20of%20Contemporary%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Karnad%20prevailed.%20In%20her%20autobiography%20%3Cem%3EJhimma%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2013)%2C%20Mehta%20recalled%20three%20moments%20that%20stunned%20the%20audience%20during%20her%201991%20run.%20These%20passages%20were%20generously%20translated%20for%20us%20by%20Shanta%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20moment%20was%20the%20opening%20scene%20of%20the%20play%2C%20as%20seventy%20or%20eighty%20twinkling%20oil%20lamps%20enter%20a%20dark%20stage.%20The%20next%20was%20the%20union%20of%20Rani%20and%20Nagaraj%2C%20%E2%80%9Cplayed%20out%20against%20the%20fervour%20and%20beat%20of%20an%20Adivasi%20song%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20their%20bodies%20twisted%2C%20turned%20and%20wound%20around%20each%20other%20without%20touching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20third%20scene%20that%20continued%20to%20haunt%20the%20audience%20was%20the%20Naga-pariksha%2C%20ordeal%20by%20snake%20venom.%20When%20Rani%20agreed%20to%20face%20the%20challenge%2C%20a%20deep%2C%20sombre%20chant%20of%20Om%20began.%20The%20collective%20voice%20of%20the%20villagers%20gathered%20around%20her%20was%20like%20the%20drone%20of%20a%20strummed%20tanpura%2C%20adding%20a%20sense%20of%20mystery%20to%20the%20event.%20The%20soft%20thumping%20of%20a%20drum%20joined%20in.%20Rani%20approached%20the%20totem%20pole%2C%20moved%20forward%2C%20recoiled%2C%20but%20then%20walked%20back%20and%20plunged%20her%20hand%20into%20the%20snake%20hole%20at%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20seemed%20to%20be%20pulling%20her%20hand%20down.%20She%20struggled%20to%20free%20it.%20When%20she%20finally%20managed%20to%20pull%20her%20hand%20out%2C%20it%20had%20turned%20into%20the%20hood%20of%20a%20cobra.%20She%20stared%20fixedly%20at%20it.%20The%20cobra%20hood%20came%20close%20to%20her%20face%2C%20slid%20around%20her%20neck%20as%20though%20to%20sting%20her%2C%20but%20caressed%20her%20instead%2C%20and%20slowly%20slithered%20down%20her%20body%20and%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20then%20the%20chanting%20and%20drumming%20had%20reached%20a%20crescendo.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20it%20stopped.%20There%20was%20a%20jubilant%20shout.%20The%20villagers%20hailed%20Rani%20as%20a%20goddess.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%E2%80%99s%201991%20production%20at%20the%20NCPA%20starred%20Bhakti%20Barve%20as%20Kurudavva%2C%20Sukanya%20Kulkarni%20as%20Rani%2C%20Sanjay%20Belose%20and%20Ganesh%20Yadav%2C%20and%20proved%20a%20runaway%20success%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03132158%2Funnamed-17.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03132158%2Funnamed-17.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03132158%2Funnamed-17-300x98.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03132158%2Funnamed-17-1024x334.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699901%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22391%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVijaya%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20Nagamandala%20(1991)%2C%20Left%3A%20Bhakti%20Barve%20as%20Kurudavva%3B%20Centre%3A%20Rani%20and%20Kurudavva%3B%20Right%3A%20Sukanya%20Kulkarni%20as%20Rani.%20Courtesy%20NCPA%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%20had%20already%20staged%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EHayavadana%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Germany%20in%201984%2C%20and%20she%20was%20now%20taking%20%3Cem%3ENagamandala%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20open%20the%20theatre%20segment%20of%20the%20Festival%20of%20India%20in%20Germany%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Leipzig%20show%2C%20though%2C%20would%20turn%20out%20quite%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20was%20not%20well%20in%20East%20Germany%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mehta%20wrote%20in%20her%20memoir.%20Budgets%20had%20been%20cut%2C%20and%20after%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Wall%2C%20actors%20and%20musicians%20had%20rushed%20off%20to%20Berlin%20to%20find%20work%20in%20films%20and%20TV.%20Bhaskar%20Chandavarkar%2C%20accustomed%20to%20working%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Symphony%20Orchestra%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20given%20three%20musicians%E2%80%A6%20from%20a%20little-known%20jazz%20band.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20show%20in%20Leipzig%20fell%20flat%20on%20its%20face.%20Nobody%20could%20be%20blamed%20for%20it.%20How%20could%20people%20be%20expected%20to%20take%20an%20interest%20in%20some%20Indian%20folk%20tale%20when%20their%20world%20was%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20radical%20political%2C%20social%20and%20cultural%20upheaval%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F9cd23982-b989-4d7e-8ef4-e1e1d19300eb%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiMTczZmEifQ.PBNXJqnQKBHgeEYkqjXtgIIV9VR-pvgw3K2feHvkCXU%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1709721865000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw0BdE73sA9unwIVKDyIEqjJ%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%253Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F9cd23982-b989-4d7e-8ef4-e1e1d19300eb%3Fj%25253DeyJ1IjoiMTczZmEifQ.PBNXJqnQKBHgeEYkqjXtgIIV9VR-pvgw3K2feHvkCXU%2526source%253Dgmail-imap%2526ust%253D1709721865000000%2526usg%253DAOvVaw0BdE73sA9unwIVKDyIEqjJ%26amp%3Bsou