F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F03%2F02%2Fus-news%2Fnypd-cop-sues-after-topless-selfie-spreads-like-wildfire%2F%3Fdicbo%3Dv2-dFJrWUk%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Alisa%20Bajraktarevic%20has%20claimed%20that%20her%20career%20has%20derailed.%20In%20her%20Manhattan%20Supreme%20Court%20lawsuit%2C%20the%2034-year-old%20NYPD%20Officer%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20force%20in%202012%2C%20informed%20that%20she%20sent%20her%20pictures%20to%20Lt%20Mark%20Rivera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20added%20that%20Ms%20Alisa%20and%20Lt%20Rivera%20dated%20for%20a%20few%20months%20in%20the%20same%20year%20when%20she%20joined%20the%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Lt%20Rivera%20allegedly%20shared%20her%20topless%20pictures%20in%20a%20group%20text%20with%20other%20cops.%20In%20no%20time%2C%20the%20photos%20began%20circulating%2C%20she%20alleged.%20Ms%20Alisa%20also%20claimed%20that%20union%20delegates%20urged%20her%20not%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20over%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20quoted%20one%20of%20the%20union%20delegates%20allegedly%20telling%20Ms%20Alisa%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20not%20the%20first%20or%20last%20woman%20this%20has%20happened%20to%20or%20would%20happen%20to.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20pictures%20resurfaced%20in%20April%20when%20Ms%20Alisa%20was%20accused%20of%20interfering%20with%20the%20officers%20who%20showed%20up%20while%20she%20was%20hanging%20out%20with%20her%20then-boyfriend%2C%20Kelvin%20Hernandez.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%20officers%20surrounded%20her%20car%20in%20the%20Bronx%2C%20prompting%20both%20Ms%20Alisa%20and%20the%2033-year-old%20to%20ask%20what%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Alisa%20denied%20that%20her%20boyfriend%20was%20selling%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hernandez%2C%20who%20was%20recording%20the%20officers%2C%20was%20charged%20with%20resisting%20arrest%2C%20according%20to%20his%20ongoing%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20department.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Mr%20Alisa%20was%20suspended%20for%20interfering%20in%20the%20traffic%20stop%20of%20her%20alleged%20drug%20dealer%20boyfriend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20further%2C%20Ms%20Alisa%20added%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20once%20the%20word%20about%20the%20aforementioned%20investigation%20was%20out%2C%20so%20were%20her%20topless%20pictures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20her%20pictures%20were%20shared%20in%20NYPD%20group%20chats%20and%20text%20message%20chains%2C%20along%20with%20personal%20information%20such%20as%20her%20parent's%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Post%2C%20Ms%20Alisa%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20do%20things%20in%20confidence.%20It%20doesn't%20warrant%20you%20being%20treated%20like%20a%20piece%20of%20s**t.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20pretty%20repulsive.%20For%2012%20years%20they%20decided%20to%20keep%20this%20on%20their%20phone%3F%20It%20spread%20like%20wildfire.%20It's%20bullying.%20I'm%20not%20the%20first%20and%20I'm%20definitely%20not%20the%20last%20but%2C%20when%20is%20it%20going%20to%20be%20enough%3F%20Because%20someone%20is%20definitely%20going%20to%20harm%20themselves%20over%20it.%20It%20feels%20like%20everything%20was%20swept%20under%20the%20rug%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20that%20NYPD%20had%20failed%20to%20investigate%20those%20who%20circulated%20her%20private%20images%20without%20her%20consent%2C%20%26quot%3Ban%20act%20which%20is%20now%20against%20the%20law%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20declining%20to%20comment%2C%20NYPD%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20tolerate%20discrimination%20or%20sexual%20harassment%20in%20any%20form%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20respectful%20work%20environments%20for%20our%20diverse%20workforce.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709454540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A