e%20Indian%20Express%2C%20said%20the%20NCA%20gave%20a%20contradictory%20fitness%20report%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20several%20media%20publications%20have%20claimed%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20attended%20a%20pre-IPL%20camp%20with%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%20This%20seems%20to%20have%20irked%20the%20BCCI%20selectors%2C%20who%20recommend%20players'%20name%20for%20central%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frevsportz.in%2Fcortisone-shots-60-ball-per-session-playing-through-pain-has-shreyas-iyer-been-treated-unfairly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevsportz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Iyer%20went%20to%20the%20KKR%20Academy%20to%20build%20his%20workload.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20playing%2060%20balls%20in%20a%20session%2C%20his%20back%20was%20building%20spasms.%20He%20had%20to%20build%20up%20his%20resistance.%20Now%20he%20is%20playing%20200%20balls%20per%20session.%20In%20three%20weeks%2C%20he%20has%20put%20on%20three%20kilos%20of%20muscles.%20The%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association%20and%20the%20Mumbai%20team%20head%20coach%20(Omkar%20Salvi)%20have%20been%20kept%20in%20the%20loop.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20coach%20visited%20the%20KKR%20Academy%20several%20times%20to%20monitor%20Iyer's%20progress.%20And%20now%20he%20has%20made%20himself%20available%20for%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20semi-final%20against%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said%20on%20conditions%20on%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20skipped%20the%20IPL%20to%20play%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Even%20after%20the%20surgery%2C%20he%20took%20three%20painkiller%20injections%20to%20be%20pain-free%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20pain%20returned%20during%20the%20semi-final%20and%20the%20final%2C%20and%20he%20played%20through%20it.%20Iyer%20was%20the%20only%20player%20who%20wasn't%20given%20a%20break%20after%20the%20World%20Cup.%20He%20played%20the%20home%20T20I%20series%20against%20Australia%20