ed%20in%20India%20during%20those%20days%20and%20had%20their%20paintings%20specifically%20designed%20for%20posters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20collectors%20go%20on%20an%20initial%20spree%20of%20collecting%20whatever%20they%20find%20interesting.%20As%20time%20goes%20by%2C%20they%20start%20researching%20on%20the%20techniques%2C%20companies%2C%20artists%2C%20styles%2C%20printers%20and%20their%20values.%20When%20the%20collection%20becomes%20large%2C%20one%20often%20tends%20to%20forget%20what%20one%20has%20acquired.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Thakral%20also%20has%20an%20enormous%20collection%20of%205%2C000%2C%20one-of-a-kind%2C%20original%20popular%20visual%20arts%20in%20the%20form%20of%20old%20calendars%2C%20posters%2C%20oleographs%20and%20prints.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20not%20to%20waste%20money%20on%20duplicates%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20catalogue%20them%2C%20so%20that%20one%20has%20a%20ready%20reckoner%20of%20what%20one%20has%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thakral.%20The%20collection%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20catalogued%20and%20maintained%20under%20the%20Tarun%20Thakral%20Archival%20collection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.43-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.43-PM.png%20864w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.43-PM-300x156.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201994%2C%20Thakral%20had%20begun%20collecting%20vintage%20and%20classic%20automobiles%20and%20related%20transport%20objects.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20collection%20grew%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20he%20was%20finding%20it%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20it.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20he%20founded%20the%20Heritage%20Transportation%20Trust%20to%20promote%20the%20preservation%20of%20modes%20of%20transportation%20that%20have%20been%20used%20in%20India.%20In%202009%2C%20he%20approached%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20to%20open%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20comprehensive%20Heritage%20Transport%20Museum%20and%20received%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%206%20crores%20to%20set%20it%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocated%20near%20Gurugram%2C%20it%20opened%20its%20doors%20to%20visitors%20in%20December%202013%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2013%20crores%20with%20funding%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20private%20and%20corporate%20donations%20as%20well%20as%20personal%20funding.%20After%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20museum%20has%20welcomed%20over%202%20million%20visitors%2C%20received%20several%20national%20and%20international%20awards%2C%20and%20been%20rated%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20museums%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121740%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.56-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121740%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.56-PM.png%20940w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03121740%2FScreenshot-2024-03-03-at-12.15.56-PM-300x152.png%20300w%5C%22%20c