o%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20ballot%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etemadonline.com%2F%25D8%25A8%25D8%25AE%25D8%25B4-%25D8%25B3%25DB%258C%25D8%25A7%25D8%25B3%25DB%258C-9%2F652287-%25D9%2587%25D8%25B4%25D8%25AF%25D8%25A7%25D8%25B1-%25D9%2586%25D8%25B8%25D8%25B1%25D8%25B3%25D9%2586%25D8%25AC%25DB%258C-%25D9%2587%25D8%25A7-%25D8%25A7%25D9%2586%25D8%25AA%25D8%25AE%25D8%25A7%25D8%25A8%25D8%25A7%25D8%25AA-%25D9%2585%25D8%25AC%25D9%2584%25D8%25B3-%25D8%25AF%25D9%2588%25D8%25A7%25D8%25B2%25D8%25AF%25D9%2587%25D9%2585%5C%22%3Erecent%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20national%20turnout%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20at%2035%25%20and%20only%2018%25%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20Tehran.%20By%20comparison%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Firandataportal.syr.edu%2F2020-parliamentary-election%5C%22%3Eturnout%20in%202020%20was%2042.5%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20but%20this%20was%20the%20lowest%20it%20had%20been%20since%201979%20and%20was%20during%20a%20global%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuccession%20question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20low%20turnout%20could%20be%20problematic%20for%20the%20political%20leadership%2C%20who%20rely%20on%20elections%20to%20provide%20a%20veil%20of%20legitimacy%20over%20their%20regime.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20supreme%20leader%2C%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20has%20started%20a%20dual%20pronged%20campaign%20of%20encouraging%20citizens%20to%20vote%20and%20blaming%20the%20west%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkhamenei_ir%2Fstatus%2F1759192438504120516%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CElections%20are%20the%20main%20pillar%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%2C%20and%20they%20are%20the%20way%20to%20improve%20the%20country.%20For%20those%20who%20are%20seeking%20to%20solve%20the%20problems%2C%20the%20way%20to%20do%20this%20is%20the%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20attended%20a%20meeting%20with%20people%20from%20the%20East%20Azerbaijan%20province%20and%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20emphasise%20that%20it%20was%20the%20intention%20of%20what%20he%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tehrantimes.com%2Fnews%2F495092%2FEnemies-oppose-Iran-elections%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Carrogant%20powers%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20US%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20boycott%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20point%20is%20that%20the%20elections%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20greater%20significance%20for%20the%20future%20of%20Islamic%20Republic%20than%20normal.%20Khamenei%20is%20currently%2084%20years%20old%2C%20so%20the%20election%20of%20the%20next%20supreme%20leader%20is%20likely%20to%20happen%20within%20the%20next%20eight-year%20term%20of%20the%20Assembly%20of%20Experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20it%20is%20thought%20that%20the%20Guardian%20Council%20has%20been%20so%20restrictive%20when%20it%20has%20come%20to%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iranintl.com%2Fen%2F202401293591%5C%22%3Ecandidate%20selection%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Assembly%20%E2%80%93%20because%20this%20election%20could%20secure%20Iranian%20succession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20results%20could%20emerge%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20although%20the%20full%20tally%20%E2%80%93%20and%20what%20it%20means%20for%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20future%20%E2%80%93%20may%20not%20be%20clear%20for%20some%20days.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F224804%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Flouise-kettle-152245%5C%22%3ELouise%20Kettle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Funiver