)%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Epazham-pori%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eelai%20adai%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3Esugiyan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0on%20offer%20at%20this%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20recent%20morning%2C%20after%20visiting%20a%20nearby%20dispensary%2C%20my%20wife%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0I%20walked%20across%20to%20the%20G-Temple%20canteen.%20I%20felt%20terribly%20guilty%20(for%20not%20paying%20obeisance%20to%20the%20deity)%20as%20I%20sat%20down%20to%20tuck%20into%20the%20crisp%20masala%20dosai%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0medhu%20vadai%20soaked%20in%20sambar.%20As%20greed%20would%20have%20it%2C%20I%20also%20ordered%20parippu%20vadai%2C%20pazham%20pori%2C%20sugiyan%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%20elai%20adai%20for%20takeaway%20%E2%80%93%20told%20myself%20that%20it%20is%20for%20my%20daughter%20Manisha%20who%20is%20visiting%20from%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20home%2C%20I%20found%20the%20sugiyan%20missing%20(the%20second%20time%20that%20my%20forgetfulness%20had%20resulted%20in%20such%20a%20situation).%20This%20made%20me%20frantic.%20I%20could%20not%20go%20back%20for%20just%20that%3B%20nor%20could%20I%20call%20the%20temple%20or%20the%20canteen%20with%20a%20petty%20request%20to%20help%20me%20get%20my%20sugiyan.%20The%20temple%20is%20particularly%20busy%20in%20the%20festive%20month%20of%20December%20when%20the%20staff%20take%20charge%20of%20the%20canteen%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0catering%2C%20besides%20providing%20an%20additional%20free%20morning%20meal%20to%20passers-by%20at%20the%20roadside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20then%20recalled%20that%2C%20while%20on%20my%20way%20back%20home%2C%20I%20had%20seen%20a%20friend%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0colleague%2C%20Mahendra%2C%20along%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20on%20a%20romantic%20walk%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20temple.%20I%20guessed%20that%20he%20too%20must%20be%20a%20devotee%20of%20the%20G-Temple%20canteen.%20I%20dialled%20him%2C%20knowing%20that%20a%20man%20tucking%20into%20dosai%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0vadai%20on%20a%20winter%20morning%20might%20not%20be%20keen%20to%20take%20the%20call%20until%20after%20the%20eating%20was%20done.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EAnd%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20I%20was%20right.%20Where%20he%20was%20wrong%20was%20in%20expecting%20that%20I%20would%20give%20up%20when%20he%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20my%20first%20attempt.%20I%20kept%20at%20it.%20Mahendra%20gave%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0took%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20spoke%20to%20the%20affable%20temple%20employee%20who%20was%20at%20the%20canteen%20counter%20on%20Mahendra%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0he%20readily%20agreed%20to%20hand%20over%20my%20forgotten%20sugiyan%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%2C%20this%20was%20Lord%20Guruvayurappan%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20letting%20me%20know%20that%20it%20never%20pays%20to%20enter%20the%20periphery%20of%20the%20sannidhi%20through%20the%20backdoor%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0exit%20through%20the%20side%20passage%2C%20thus%20bypassing%20the%20presiding%20deity%20of%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20I%20feel%20blessed.%20Actually%2C%20like%20mercy%20(not%20the%20late%20Rev%20S%20Kappen%E2%80%99s%20niece%20in%20Bombay)%2C%20I%20feel%20twice%20blessed%3A%20for%20the%20direct%20benefit%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0also%20for%20the%20opportunity%20of%20a%20Direct%20Benefit%20Transfer%20(DBT)%20to%20Mahendra.%20May%20the%20Lord%20continue%20to%20have%20mercy%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EP.S.%20Mahendra%20thinks%20I%20was%20getting%20back%20at%20him%20for%20the%20time%20when%20he%20had%20phoned%20me%20to%20collect%20the%20pastries%20which%20he%20had%20ordered%20at%20the%20IIC%20confectionery%20counter%20but%20forgot%20to%20pick%20up%20on%20his%20way%20out.%20I%20would%20opt%20for%20a%20sugiyan%20over%20a%20walnut%20brownie%20any%20day!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShastri%20Ramachandaran%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F6a56b0a4-4ab2-4f00-b6a2-3b6920f08fda%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709447955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fguruvayurappans-grace%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20I%20learnt%20that%20it%20never%20pays%20to%20enter%20the%20periphery%20of%20the%20sannidhi%20through%20the%20backdoor%C2%A0and%C2%A0exit%20through%20the%20side%20passage%2C%20thus%20bypassing%20the%20presiding%20deity%20of%20a%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fguruvayurappans-grace%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20IPL%20vs%20Test%20Debate%2C%20Ganguly%20Namedrops%20Dravid%2C%20Sachin%20In%20Massive%20Take%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20an%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20career%20can%20exist%20for%20a%20cricketer%20alongside%20stints%20in%20first-class%20cricket.%20Amid%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20BCCI%20not%20offering%20central%20contracts%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kisha