%20The%20woman%2C%2028%2C%20was%20allegedly%20gang-raped%20by%20seven%20men%20when%20she%20was%20spending%20the%20night%20with%20her%20partner%20in%20a%20makeshift%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20journey%2C%20from%20Bangladesh%20on%20two%20motorcycles%2C%20was%20intended%20to%20continue%20through%20Bihar%20and%20ultimately%20reach%20Nepal.%20However%2C%20the%20woman%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20attacked%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20has%20happened%20to%20us%20that%20we%20would%20not%20wish%20on%20anyone.%20Seven%20men%20have%20raped%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20shared%20on%20social%20media%2C%20along%20with%20images%20showing%20horrific%20injuries%20to%20her%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20and%20her%20partner%2C%2064%2C%20later%20took%20down%20the%20video%20from%20social%20media%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20Jharkhand%20Police%20asked%20them%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bdisturb%26quot%3B%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20told%20me%20to%20turn%20off%20the%20post%20so%20as%20not%20to%20disturb%20the%20investigation.%20I%20will%20post%20it%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20shared%20on%20her%20Instagram%20stories.%20In%20a%20video%20uploaded%20to%20her%20stories%20the%20woman's%20face%20can%20be%20seen%20swollen%20and%20bruised%20following%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20face%20looks%20like%20this%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20what%20hurts%20me%20the%20most.%20I%20thought%20we%20were%20going%20to%20die.%20Thank%20God%20we%20are%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManhunt%20On%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20arrested%20three%20men%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20the%20crime.%20A%20manhunt%20is%20now%20underway%20to%20apprehend%20the%20remaining%20accused.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20has%20been%20constituted%20to%20ensure%20a%20thorough