%20law%20and%20order%20machinery%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20incident%20came%20up%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20Assembly%20during%20its%20concluding%20day%20of%20the%20budget%20session%2C%20leading%20to%20adjournments%20and%20heated%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20finger-pointing%20gained%20momentum%20with%20the%20Opposition%20demanding%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20Dumka%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20probe%20committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709446560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Foot8t25k_police-generic_625x300_07_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthought-we-were-going-to-die-spanish-tourist-gang-raped-in-jharkhand-5167053%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%2C%2028%2C%20was%20allegedly%20gang-raped%20by%20seven%20men%20when%20she%20was%20spending%20the%20night%20with%20her%20partner%20in%20a%20makeshift%20tent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthought-we-were-going-to-die-spanish-tourist-gang-raped-in-jharkhand-5167053%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthought-we-were-going-to-die-spanish-tourist-gang-raped-in-jharkhand-5167053%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthought-we-were-going-to-die-spanish-tourist-gang-raped-in-jharkhand-5167053%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Students%20Kiss%2C%20Lick%20Each%20Other's%20Toes%20At%20US%20School%20Fundraiser%2C%20Probe%20Ordered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20shocking%20video%20of%20students%20in%20the%20United%20States%20sucking%20and%20licking%20one%20another's%20toes%20at%20an%20Oklahoma%20school-sanctioned%20fundraiser%20went%20viral%20online%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F03%2F02%2Fus-news%2Foklahoma-teens-lick-each-others-toes-at-school-sanctioned-event-video-shows%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dnypost%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20disturbing%20video%2C%20at%20least%20four%20Deer%20Creek%20High%20School%20students%20are%20shown%20furiously%20licking%20peanut%20butter%20off%20their%20classmates'%20bare%20feet%20while%20lying%20on%20their%20stomachs%20on%20what%20looks%20to%20be%20a%20gym%20floor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%F0%9F%9A%A8GRAPHIC%20WARNING-Deer%20Creek%20High%20students%20in%20Oklahoma%2C%20kiss%20and%20suck%20donors'%20feet%20at%20a%20strange%20ritual%20%E2%80%9Ccharity%E2%80%9D%20event.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20a%20parent%2C%20would%20you%20allow%20your%20child%20to%20participate%20in%20something%20as%20grotesque%20as%20this%3F%20%F0%9F%A4%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaKHqNdI07y%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FaKHqNdI07y%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20VINCENT%20OSHANA%20(%40VincentOshana)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVincentOshana%2Fstatus%2F1763917314263580829%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20students%20are%20seen%20cheering%20for%20the%20participants%20as%20moderators%20watch%20the%20bizarre%20competition.%20A%20student%20is%20heard%20saying%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20devouring%20those!%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20gained%20millions%20of%20views%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20prompted%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20Oklahoma%20State%20Department%20of%20Education.%20Oklahoma%20State%20Superintendent%20Ryan%20Walters%20took%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20and%20reacted%20to%20the%20horrifying%20footage.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20disgusting.%20We%20are%20cleaning%20up%20this%20filth%20in%20Oklahoma%20schools.%20Our%20agency%20is%20investigating.%26quot%3B%20In%20another%20post%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20child%20abuse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Deer%20Creek%20School%20District%2C%20the%20video%20was%20shot%20on%20February%2029%202024%2C%20during%20the%20Clash%20of%20Classes%20assembly%2C%20which%20was%20a%20component%20of%20the%20high%20school's%20week-long%20fundraising%20campaign%20for%20a%20nearby%20coffee%20shop%20that%20hires%20individuals%20with%20special%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20from%20classes%209th%20to%2012th%20volunteered%20their%20time%20to%20take%20part%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20class%20competitions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20toe-sucking%20tournament%2C%20which%20their%20classmates%20paid%20to%20attend.%20After%20praising%20students%20for%20their%20participation%20in%20the%20school's%20Wonderful%20Week%20of%20Fundraising%2C%20which%20raised%20%24152%2C830.38%2C%20administrators%20then%20issued%20an%20apology%20to%20the%20parents%20and%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20district%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20video%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20of%20one%20of%20the%20activities%20that%20involves%20students%20only%20during%20this%20assembly%20that%20has%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20gained%20national%20attention.%20We%20want%20to%20stress%20to%20our%20community%20that%20much%20of%20the%20information%20accompanying%20this%20video%20is%20inaccurate.%20However%2C%20through%20this%20specific%20game%20we%20failed%20to%20uphold%20the%20dignity%20of%20our%20students%20and%20the%20proud%20image%20of%20our%20community.%20We%20have%20a%20responsibility%20to%20protect%20our%20Antlers%20and%20showcase%20them%20in%20a%20positive%20light.%20In%20regards%20to%20this%20one%20particular%20activity%2C%20we%20fell%20short%20and%20for%20that%20we%20greatly%20apologize.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20standing%20with%20us%20and%20helping%20us%20to%20weather%20this%20storm%20and%20move%20forward%20together.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20surprising.%20I%20didn't%20think%20they%20were%20going%20to%20do%20all%20that.%20I%20was%20just%20shocked.%20I%20didn't%20really%20have%20like%20a%20feeling.%20I%20was%20kind%20of%20disgusted%2C%20and%20then%20kind%20of%20glad%20I%20wasn't%20over%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20she%20told%20me%20yesterday%20that%20was%20happening%2C%20I%20had%20to%20ask%20her%2C%20'Wait%2C%20what%3F%20They're%20licking%20peanut%20butter%20off%20of%20toes.%20What%3F%20I%20am%20all%20for%20fundraising%20and%20all%20for%20really%20fun%20and%20silly%20things%2C%20but%20that%20right%20there%20just%20seems%20a%20little%20excessive%26quot%3B%20a%20parent%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parent%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20great%20that%20they%20raised%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20I%20feel%20like%20maybe%20they%20could've%20done%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20accountability%20and%20ownership%20in%20that%20statement%20for%2C%20'Hey%2C%20you%20know%2C%20maybe%20we%20didn't%20fully%20think%20this%20thing%20through%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20videos%20have%20amassed%20several%20reactions%20on%20social%20media.%20Many%20labelled%20the%20act%20as%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20in%20high%20school%2C%20we%20sold%20candy%20to%20raise%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20fresh%20hell%20is%20this%3F%3F%20This%20is%20beyond%20degrading!!%26quot%3B%20commented%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20teachers%20were%20like%20yea%20this%20is%20ok%20lol%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisgusting%20and%20who%20chose%20to%20have%20kids%20engage%20in%20this%20for%20a%20fundraiser%3F%20These%20teachers%20and%20or%20ad