e%20village%E2%80%99s%20plight%20continued%20until%202019%20when%20Meenakshi%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20village%20head.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%20Gadge%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20village%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20sarpanch%20madam%20had%20been%20advocating%20for%20social%20work%20from%20the%20time%20when%20she%20was%20not%20even%20elected%20as%20the%20village%20head.%20And%20today%20her%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%20a%20behavioural%20change%20among%20the%20community.%20We%20not%20only%20use%20the%20toilets%20in%20our%20homes%20but%20are%20also%20aware%20of%20how%20to%20segregate%20our%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%2C%20who%20also%20works%20with%20the%20mandal%20parishad%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20constituency%20of%20the%20village%2C%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20village%20has%20become%20a%20model%20for%20408%20gram%20panchayats%20in%20the%20state.%20Today%2C%20many%20sarpanches%20from%20other%20districts%20visit%20our%20village%20to%20witness%20how%20we%20achieved%20this%20transformation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20village%20has%20utilised%20Rs%2036%20crores%20as%20funds%20from%20the%20state%20and%20the%20central%20government%20to%20successfully%20implement%20various%20government%20programmes%20and%20achieve%20the%20change.%20Other%20than%20the%20official%20help%2C%20Meenakshi%20credits%20the%20community%20for%20the%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20panchayat%20is%20entitled%20to%20the%20same%20funds%20but%20we%20stood%20apart%20from%20them%20because%20we%20utilised%20them%20for%20betterment.%20But%20this%20success%20could%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20at%20the%20individual%20level.%20Only%20when%20you%20involve%20the%20community%20and%20give%20them%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%2C%20can%20you%20achieve%20a%20drastic%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%