one%20of%20my%20dogs%20passes%20away%2C%20I%20tell%20Gerry%20that%20I%20want%20to%20shut%20the%20shelter%20down.%20Recently%2C%20I%20lost%20a%20German%20Shepherd%20called%20Zain.%20He%20was%20my%20dearest%20baby.%20He%20came%20to%20us%20as%20a%20three-month-old%20pup%20with%20his%20pelvis%20crushed%20and%20by%20the%20time%20he%20was%20ten%20months%20old%2C%20he%20had%20become%20this%20massive%20fellow%20following%20me%20around%20everywhere.%20We%20name%20all%20the%20dogs%20in%20our%20shelter%20and%20choose%20them%20according%20to%20their%20personality.%20I%E2%80%99m%20still%20grieving%20for%20that%20boy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20an%20old%20dog%20stays%20with%20us%20for%20two%20months%20and%20passes%20away%2C%20it%20tears%20me%20up%20from%20within.%20I%E2%80%99m%20shattered%20for%20the%20next%20few%20days%20until%20I%20see%20a%20video%20of%20another%20dog%20or%20puppy%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Chennai%20who%20needs%20our%20assistance.%20I%20focus%20my%20energy%20on%20helping%20that%20dog.%20I%20find%20a%20way%20to%20block%20that%20pain%20by%20immersing%20myself%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20other%20dogs%20in%20our%20care.%20But%20it%20also%20gives%20me%20great%20joy%20seeing%20these%20dogs%20get%20shelter%2C%20recover%2C%20and%20play%20around%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3ESarah%20needs%20your%20assistance%20to%20maintain%20her%20shelter%20for%20old%2C%20abandoned%2C%20disabled%20and%20paraplegic%20dogs.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20contribute%2C%20click%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilaap.org%2Fstories%2Fhelp-paraplegic-and-blind-dogs-and-pups-tb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3sMCfMy-r1%2F%3Futm_source%3D